Problem URL - https://leetcode.com/problems/project-employees-i/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-sql-50

SOLUTION - 

  /* Write your T-SQL query statement below */


SELECT p.project_id, COALESCE(ROUND(CAST(SUM(experience_years) AS FLOAT)/COUNT(*),2), 0.00) as average_years
FROM Project p
LEFT JOIN Employee e
ON p.employee_id = e.employee_id
GROUP BY p.project_id
